 The convoy of deposed Emir of Kano Muhammadu Sanusi II has arrived Awe in Awe local government area of Nasarawa from Loko where he was initially taken to following his banishment. He was moved to Awe on Tuesday afternoon reportedly because of lack of social amenities in the town after a seven-hour grueling drive from Kano. His convoy arrived Awe town around 6: 55pm.  Details shortlyâ€¦